Gross Revenue    {gross_revenue}
- Product Cost   {product_cost} ({product_cost_pct}%)
- Amazon Fees    {amazon_fees} ({amazon_fees_pct}%)
- Advertising    {advertising} ({advertising_pct}%)
= Net Profit     {net_profit} ({margin_pct}%)

BY PRODUCT:
{product_bars}

BUY BOX %:
{buy_box_bars}""" ;
    oc:templateVariables "advertising",
        "advertising_pct",
        "amazon_fees",
        "amazon_fees_pct",
        "buy_box_bars",
        "gross_revenue",
        "margin_pct",
        "mom_change",
        "net_profit",
        "orders",
        "orders_change",
        "product_bars",
        "product_cost",
        "product_cost_pct",
        "revenue",
        "units",
        "units_change" .

oc:kn_44d3f8fb a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:Procedure ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When executing the core Amazon seller operations cycle" ;
    oc:directiveContent "1. Optimize listings (keywords, images, A+ content) 2. Monitor Buy Box and maintain competitive pricing 3. Manage inventory to avoid stockouts and excess 4. Control ACoS to optimize PPC efficiency 5. Respond to messages within 24 hours 6. Track daily sales and profit metrics 7. Plan inventory for seasonal peaks (Q4) 8. Stay compliant with Amazon policies" ;
    oc:stepOrder 1 .

oc:kn_44ed0b25 a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:Prerequisite ;
    oc:directiveContent "Requires Amazon Selling Partner API (SP-API) credentials and the ecommerce-mcp server with amazon_sp_api, amazon_ads_api, amazon_inventory, and amazon_orders tools configured." .

oc:kn_5cce522d a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:OutputFormat ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When generating FBA inventory status reports" ;
    oc:directiveContent """FBA INVENTORY STATUS
═══════════════════════════════════════

OVERVIEW:
Total SKUs:        {total_skus}
In Stock:          {in_stock}
Low Stock:         {low_stock}
Out of Stock:      {out_of_stock}

INVENTORY HEALTH:
Healthy           {healthy_pct}%
Excess            {excess_pct}%
Stranded          {stranded_pct}%
Aged (180+ days)  {aged_pct}%

TOP SELLERS (Days of Supply):
┌──────────────────┬───────────┬──────────┐
│ Product          │ Stock     │ Days     │
└──────────────────┴───────────┴──────────┘

RECOMMENDED ACTIONS:
• {action_1}
• {action_2}
• {action_3}""" ;
    oc:templateVariables "action_1",
        "action_2",
        "action_3",
        "aged_pct",
        "excess_pct",
        "healthy_pct",
        "in_stock",
        "low_stock",
        "out_of_stock",
        "stranded_pct",
        "total_skus" .

oc:kn_612e9bc1 a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:SideEffect ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When executing automated pricing, inventory, or advertising actions" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Dynamic pricing adjustments modify live listing prices. Inventory shipment plans create Amazon logistics orders. PPC bid changes immediately affect ad delivery and spend." ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

oc:kn_63265705 a oc:Constraint,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When creating or optimizing Amazon product listings" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Product titles must be under 200 characters, with capitalized first words, no promotional phrases, and include main keywords. Backend keywords are limited to 250 bytes with no punctuation or repeated words." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Amazon enforces strict listing compliance; violations can result in suppressed listings or account suspension." ;
    oc:severityLevel "CRITICAL" .

oc:kn_640d13f1 a oc:CodePattern,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When interacting with Amazon SP-API for orders, inventory, and fee estimation" ;
    oc:codeLanguage "python" ;
    oc:directiveContent """# List Orders
orders = sp_api.orders.get_orders(
    MarketplaceIds=["ATVPDKIKX0DER"],
    CreatedAfter="2024-01-01T00:00:00Z",
    OrderStatuses=["Unshipped", "PartiallyShipped"]
)

# Create Inbound Shipment Plan
sp_api.fba_inventory.create_inbound_shipment_plan(
    ShipFromAddress=warehouse_address,
    InboundShipmentPlanRequestItems=[{"SellerSKU": "PROD-001", "Quantity": 500}]
)

# Get Product Fees
fees = sp_api.products.get_my_fees_estimate_for_sku(
    SellerSKU="PROD-001",
    MarketplaceId="ATVPDKIKX0DER",
    PriceToEstimateFees={"ListingPrice": {"Amount": 29.99}}
)""" .

oc:kn_93271783 a oc:AntiPattern,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When configuring dynamic pricing or competing for Buy Box" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Never price below the minimum profit floor (cost + fees) even when competing for the Buy Box. Always set a floor price in dynamic pricing rules." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Selling below cost destroys margins and can trigger a race-to-the-bottom with competitors that is difficult to recover from." ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

oc:kn_965716e0 a oc:Heuristic,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When reviewing aged inventory" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Inventory aged over 180 days should trigger removal orders, promotions, or price adjustments to avoid escalating long-term storage fees." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Amazon charges significantly higher storage fees for aged inventory, eroding profitability on slow-moving products." .

oc:kn_a19a6882 a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:KnownIssue ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When making frequent SP-API calls" ;
    oc:directiveContent "SP-API rate limits can be hit when bulk-updating listings or pulling large order reports. Implement exponential backoff and batch operations." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Amazon enforces strict rate limits per operation; exceeding them causes 429 errors that halt automation workflows." .

oc:kn_a3aa1df4 a oc:DesignPrinciple,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When setting up or optimizing Amazon PPC advertising" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Use a tiered PPC campaign structure: auto campaigns for keyword discovery ($20/day), exact match for top performers ($50/day), phrase for mid-performers ($30/day), and broad for discovery ($20/day). Target ACoS of 25%." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Tiered campaigns balance discovery and efficiency—auto campaigns feed keyword data into higher-budget exact match campaigns while maintaining cost control through ACoS targets." .

oc:kn_be6fa48e a oc:KnowledgeNode,
        oc:PreFlightCheck ;
    oc:appliesToContext "Before running any Amazon seller automation workflow" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Verify SP-API credentials are active, marketplace IDs are correct (e.g., ATVPDKIKX0DER for US), and rate limit budgets are available before executing bulk operations." .

oc:kn_ef4b0d47 a oc:Constraint,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When handling buyer-seller messaging" ;
    oc:directiveContent "All customer messages must receive a response within 24 hours per Amazon Seller Central policy." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Failure to respond within 24 hours impacts seller metrics and can result in account health warnings or suspension." ;
    oc:severityLevel "CRITICAL" .

